Dialogue: 3,0:00:30.10,0:00:34.10,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}告知冬天来临的风声 
Dialogue: 3,0:00:34.89,0:00:38.89,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}侧耳聆听 身躯颤抖
Dialogue: 3,0:00:42.00,0:00:46.00,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}一旁的你吐出的气息 
Dialogue: 3,0:00:47.60,0:00:51.60,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}白茫茫地感觉很冷
Dialogue: 3,0:00:55.20,0:00:59.20,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}今年 生命又走到了尽头
Dialogue: 3,0:00:59.20,0:01:03.20,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}引颈期盼那未来的春天
Dialogue: 3,0:01:05.90,0:01:09.90,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}边倾听着生命的连续
Dialogue: 3,0:01:11.59,0:01:15.59,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}新芽不断冒出 在光芒中
Dialogue: 3,0:01:16.70,0:01:20.70,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}就是知道这走向腐朽的命运
Dialogue: 3,0:01:21.00,0:01:25.00,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}才要更加坚强
Dialogue: 3,0:01:25.09,0:01:29.09,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}我还想继续呼吸 我还想继续歌唱
Dialogue: 3,0:01:29.29,0:01:33.29,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}真希望我能够留下些什么
Dialogue: 3,0:01:36.90,0:01:40.90,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}能代表我活过的生命证明…
Dialogue: 3,0:01:44.00,0:01:48.00,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}我不想让这变成一首悲伤的歌
Dialogue: 3,0:01:51.59,0:01:55.59,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}哪 拜托 就只要在这一刻 
Dialogue: 3,0:01:58.50,0:02:02.50,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}让我能够保持微笑… 我想在你的身旁
Dialogue: 3,0:02:03.29,0:02:07.29,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}唱起一首 温柔的歌
Dialogue: 3,0:02:40.00,0:02:44.00,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}不知经过了几个冬天
Dialogue: 3,0:02:45.80,0:02:49.80,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}才终于注意到 这份心情
Dialogue: 3,0:02:52.30,0:02:56.30,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}虽然没有办法对你表白
Dialogue: 3,0:02:57.80,0:03:01.80,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}但我们的心总是相系的喔…
Dialogue: 3,0:03:03.69,0:03:07.69,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}太黑暗什么也看不见… 
Dialogue: 3,0:03:07.80,0:03:11.80,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}什么也听不见…
Dialogue: 3,0:03:10.40,0:03:14.40,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 836)\fs57}好害怕
Dialogue: 3,0:03:12.09,0:03:16.09,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 836)\fs57}好痛苦
Dialogue: 3,0:03:13.30,0:03:17.30,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 836)\fs57}好寂寞
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.40,0:03:21.40,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}一切的一切都
Dialogue: 3,0:03:19.30,0:03:23.30,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 836)\fs57}逐渐消逝之中
Dialogue: 3,0:03:22.30,0:03:26.30,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 836)\fs57}此刻只有你的笑容
Dialogue: 3,0:03:28.40,0:03:32.40,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}没有消失…
Dialogue: 3,0:03:32.69,0:03:36.69,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}要继续唱着温柔的歌喔
Dialogue: 3,0:03:37.09,0:03:41.09,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}就算被孤寂的世界 包围
Dialogue: 3,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.50,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}我永远都会在你身边喔 不要忘了
Dialogue: 3,0:03:50.19,0:03:54.19,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}你永远都不会是
Dialogue: 3,0:03:53.30,0:03:57.30,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 836)\fs57}一个人哟
Dialogue: 3,0:04:20.69,0:04:24.69,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}我一点都不寂寞 因为有你在
Dialogue: 3,0:04:27.10,0:04:31.10,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}紧紧地抱住我 用那温暖的双手
Dialogue: 3,0:04:33.60,0:04:37.60,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}虽然听不到 但我收到了 从触碰的指尖传来的
Dialogue: 3,0:04:43.19,0:04:47.19,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)}我爱你。。。
Dialogue: 3,0:04:47.69,0:04:51.69,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}我不想让这变成一首悲伤的歌
Dialogue: 3,0:04:54.69,0:04:58.69,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}哪 拜托 就只要在这一刻
Dialogue: 3,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.50,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}我想要唱下去 跟你一起 
Dialogue: 3,0:05:06.80,0:05:10.80,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}唱着那首 温柔的歌。。。
Dialogue: 3,0:05:14.19,0:05:18.19,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}想要献给你 一首离别之歌。。。
Dialogue: 3,0:05:19.69,0:05:23.69,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)\fs57}在最后我想告诉你。。。
Dialogue: 3,0:05:26.50,0:05:30.50,AcplayDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(960, 900)}谢谢你。。。
